If you want authentic,  then this is the best place for it.. I have gone to Ali Baba roughly 20 times in the last 3 years.. every.single.time..... they make the best, freshest and most authentic food you can get in the French quarter.  They aren't trying to be a fancy French restaurant,  or some other "new Orleans " favorite. They are not over-priced. They sell great food, and get it to you fast. Hands down, this is where you should stop after a great night in the Quarter.
